<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7415> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7415" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Quaestor of the consul L. Calpurnius Bestia in 111 (Sall. lug. 29.4-6; MRR 1.541, 543, note 4). He should more probably be identified with C. Sextius C. f. Calvinus (21), Pr. ca. 92 (see ILLRP 291; MRR 2.18) than with P. Sextius (9), who was convicted toward 90 of ambitus while pr. desig. (Cic. Brut. 180). See Sumner, Orators 76-77.[198x]\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/3442> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #3442" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Served under the Consul Bestia in Numidia (Sall. Iug. 29.4; cf. Cic. Brut. 180)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/3441> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #3441" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "He may possibly be identified with the P. Sextius (RE no. 9), Praetorelect who was convicted of bribery toward 90 B.C. (Cic. Brut. 180)." .
